166
0:07:07.782,000 --> 0:07:09,000
et sa gourmandise nationale.

167
0:07:09.878,000 --> 0:07:11,000
Si vous venez d'Islande,

168
0:07:11.93,000 --> 0:07:12,000
votre plat national

169
0:07:13.254,000 --> 0:07:15,000
